me; see [32]. Moreover, the character F [i] can be determined in O (logÏƒ) time by a binary search on C ,4 or, using n+o(n)
tra bits, by a constant time rank query. Since S[SA[rb]] = F [rb], S[SA[rb] + 1] = F [Ïˆ(rb)], S[SA[rb] + 2] = F [Ïˆ(Ïˆ(rb))]
